scripts.comment: This is the code for the banana. When the banana is touching green, it sends a broadcast to the monkey to let the monkey know that it missed the banana. Then the banana's position is reset. When the banana receives the broadcast to reset, reset the banana's position, and make it fall (25 units downwards every 0.1 secs).

This is the code for the monkey. Clicking the green flag will reset the monkey's position and signal for the banana to reset itself. Pressing the left arrow key will move the monkey left by 10 steps, and pressing right will move the monkey right 10 steps. When the monkey receives the signal that it has missed a banana, it says, "Noo I missed a banana!" When the monkey touches a banana, it send a broadcast to signal for the banana to reset itself, and the monkey says, "Yum!"
